:\"Vagelis\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5850:\"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-1024x683.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-923\" srcset=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-1024x683.png 1024w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-300x200.png 300w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-768x512.png 768w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-1536x1024.png 1536w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/04/wp20-web-banner-1-2048x1365.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"#english\" data-type=\"internal\" data-id=\"#english\"><strong>[english version below]</strong><br></a>Το WordPress φέτος γίνεται 20 χρονών! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f973.png\" alt=\"🥳\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Ελάτε να γιορτάσουμε την επέτειο των “γενεθλίων” του, να κάνουμε μια ανασκόπηση της πορείας του WordPress και της εξέλιξης που είχε αυτά τα 20 χρόνια αλλά και να συζητήσουμε το τι επιφυλάσει το μέλλον. Θα έχουμε καφέ, αναψυκτικά, διάφορα σνακς και φυσικά τούρτα! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f370.png\" alt=\"🍰\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Θα σας περιμένουμε όλους το Σάββατο 27 Μαΐου 2023 στις 13:00, στο ΙΕΚ ΑΛΦΑ, σε έναν όμορφο και ανακαινισμένο χώρο! Η συμμετοχή είναι ανοιχτή για όλους και απολύτως δωρεάν!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4c5.png\" alt=\"📅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Σάββατο, 27 Μαΐου 2023<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f55b.png\" alt=\"🕛\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> 13:00<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5fa.png\" alt=\"🗺\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Ι.Ε.Κ. ΑΛΦΑ, Βαλαωρίτου 9, 54626 Θεσσαλονίκη</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/293104685/\">https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/293104685/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ευχαριστούμε τους παρακάτω χορηγούς για την έμπρακτη στήριξη της εκδήλωσης:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Θερμές ευχαριστίες στo ΙΕΚ ΑΛΦΑ Θεσσαλονίκης, που στηρίζει την ελληνική κοινότητα του WordPress και μας προσφέρει δωρεάν τον πολύ όμορφο χώρο τους για όλα μας τα meetup. Λειτουργεί στο κέντρο της Θεσσαλονίκης σε σύγχρονες εγκαταστάσεις ειδικά διαμορφωμένες για τις ανάγκες ενός σύγχρονου ΙΕΚ.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Weglot is one of the best WordPress multilingual plugin to translate and display your website in multiple languages.<br>Founded in 2016, Weglot is trusted by more than 50,000 websites owners and developers, with an average rating of 4.9/5.0 (700+ reviews).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>***</p>\n\n\n\n<p id=\"english\"><strong>[english version]</strong><br>WordPress is turning 20 years old this year! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f973.png\" alt=\"🥳\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Join us to celebrate its &#8220;birthday&#8221;, look back at WordPress&#8217;s journey and the progress it has made over the past 20 years, and discuss what the future holds. We will have coffee, soft drinks, various snacks, and of course cake! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f370.png\" alt=\"🍰\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We will be waiting for you all on Saturday, May 27th, 2023, at 1:00 pm at IEK ALFA, in a beautiful and renovated space! Participation is open to everyone and completely free!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4c5.png\" alt=\"📅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Saturday May 27th 2023<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f55b.png\" alt=\"🕛\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> 1:00pm<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5fa.png\" alt=\"🗺\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> ΙΕΚ ALFA, 9 Valaoritou str., 54626 Thessaloniki</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/293104685/\">https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/293104685/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We would like to thank the following sponsors for supporting this event:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A big thank you to&nbsp;<strong>IEK ALFA of Thessaloniki</strong>, that supports the WordPress Greek Community and offers their very nice space for all of our meetups. IEK ALFA operates in the city center of Thessaloniki, and features modern facilities, specially formatted to accommodate the needs of a modern IEK.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Weglot</strong>&nbsp;is one of the best WordPress multilingual plugin to translate and display your website in multiple languages.<br>Founded in 2016, Weglot is trusted by more than 50,000 websites owners and developers, with an average rating of 4.9/5.0 (700+ reviews).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/293104685/attendees/\"></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://el.wordpress.org/2023/04/24/thessaloniki-wordpress-meetup-wp20/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"c