 δημιουργίας&#160;SEO content σε e-commerce sites! Μετά την ενδιαφέρουσα ομιλία, θα γίνει και η κοπή της πίτας! Τι και εάν πέρασαν ήδη δύο μήνες; Ποτέ δεν είναι αργά 😀Spoiler: [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Vagelis\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6053:\"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-903\" srcset=\"https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup-300x169.jpg 300w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup-768x432.jpg 768w, https://el.wordpress.org/files/2023/02/31st-Meetup.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>[english version below]</strong><br>Το 31ο Thessaloniki WordPress Meetup έρχεται <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Μαζί μας θα είναι ο Αντώνης Δημητρίου, SEO strategist στη Minuttia, ο οποίος θα μας μιλήσει&nbsp;<strong>για τη στρατηγική δημιουργίας</strong>&nbsp;SEO content σε e-commerce sites!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Μετά την ενδιαφέρουσα ομιλία, θα γίνει και η κοπή της πίτας! Τι και εάν πέρασαν ήδη δύο μήνες; Ποτέ δεν είναι αργά <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f600.png\" alt=\"😀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><br><em>Spoiler: Θα υπάρχουν πολλά “φλουριά” με ενδιαφέροντα δωράκια!</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Σας περιμένουμε όλους το Σάββατο 4 Μαρτίου, στις 12:00, στο Ι.Ε.Κ. Άλφα σε έναν όμορφο και ανακαινισμένο χώρο, με καφεδάκι, χυμούς και αναψυκτικά και φυσικά πολύ WordPress! Η συμμετοχή είναι ανοιχτή για όλους και απολύτως δωρεάν!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4c5.png\" alt=\"📅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Σάββατο, 4 Μαρτίου 2023<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f55b.png\" alt=\"🕛\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> 12:00<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5fa.png\" alt=\"🗺\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Ι.Ε.Κ. Άλφα, Βαλαωρίτου 9, 54626 Θεσσαλονίκη</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/291715225/\">https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/291715225/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ευχαριστούμε τους παρακάτω χορηγούς για την έμπρακτη στήριξη της εκδήλωσης:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Θερμές ευχαριστίες στo ΙΕΚ ΑΛΦΑ Θεσσαλονίκης, που στηρίζουν την ελληνική κοινότητα του WordPress και μας προσφέρουν δωρεάν τον πολύ όμορφο χώρο τους για όλα μας τα meetup. Λειτουργεί στο κέντρο της Θεσσαλονίκης σε σύγχρονες εγκαταστάσεις ειδικά διαμορφωμένες για τις ανάγκες ενός σύγχρονου ΙΕΚ.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Weglot is one of the best WordPress multilingual plugin to translate and display your website in multiple languages.<br>Founded in 2016, Weglot is trusted by more than 50,000 websites owners and developers, with an average rating of 4.9/5.0 (700+ reviews).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>[english version]</strong><br>The 31st Thessaloniki WordPress Meetup is coming <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" />We will have with us Antonis Dimitriou, SEO Strategist at Minuttia, who will talk about the strategy of creating SEO content on e-commerce sites!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>After the interesting talk, the new-year cake will be served! It’s been two months already but it’s never too late <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f600.png\" alt=\"😀\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><br><em>Spoiler: There will be many &#8220;lucky coins&#8221; and interesting gifts!</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We will be awaiting each and every one of you on Saturday, March 4th, at 12:00 (noon), at IEK Alfa, in a nice and renovated space, with coffee, juices, sodas and of course a lot of WordPress! Participation is open to everyone and completely free!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4c5.png\" alt=\"📅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Saturday, March 4th 2023<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f55b.png\" alt=\"🕛\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> 12:00 (noon)<br><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5fa.png\" alt=\"🗺\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> IEK Alfa, 9 Valaoritou str, 54626 Thessaloniki</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/291715225/\">https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/291715225/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>We would like to thank the following sponsors for supporting this event:<br>A big thank you to&nbsp;<strong>IEK ALFA of Thessaloniki</strong>, that supports the WordPress Greek Community and offers their very nice space for all of our meetups. IEK ALFA operates in the city center of Thessaloniki, and features modern facilities, specially formatted to accommodate the needs of a modern IEK.<br><strong>Weglot</strong>&nbsp;is one of the best WordPress multilingual plugin to translate and display your website in multiple languages.<br>Founded in 2016, Weglot is trusted by more than 50,000 websites owners and developers, with an average rating of 4.9/5.0 (700+ reviews).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress_skg/events/291715225/attendees/\"></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://el.wordpress.org/2023/02/20/31st-thessaloniki-wordpress-meetup/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"30th Thessaloniki WordPress Meetup\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://el.wordpress.org/2023/01/31/30th-thessaloniki-wordpress-meetup/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://el.wordpress.org/2023/01/31/30th-thessaloniki-wordpress-meetup/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 20:44:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"community\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"da